Titolo: Mega Man Zero Collection

Anno: 2010

Descrizione: Mega Man Zero Collection is a compilation of all four Mega Man Zero video games, which were originally released for the Game Boy Advance between 2002 and 2005. It was developed by Inti Creates and published by Capcom, and was made available worldwide in June 2010 for the Nintendo DS. The collection contains new features such as a beginner-friendly "Easy Scenario" that grants power-up items and abilities from the beginning of each game, as well as unlockable character art and the ability to display artwork on the Nintendo DS's bottom screen as the game is played.
In 2020, an updated version of the collection titled the Mega Man Zero/ZX Legacy Collection was released for PlayStation 4, Xbox One, Nintendo Switch and PC (Steam), adding in Mega Man ZX and Mega Man ZX Advent as well as new additional features.